==Origin==
[[Rumor|Rumors]] on the internets suggest that the first sightings of this [[forced meme]] date back to [[Last_Thursday|March 2007]]. Since then several variations of it have been spammed over and over again on [[/b/]]. Spinoffs include the thread starting with '[[Rickroll|WE'RE NO STRANGERS TO LOVE]]', '[[Shit_nobody_cares_about|ON A DARK DESERT HIGHWAY]]', '[[TL;DR|I HEARD THAT YOU WERE TALKING SHIT AND YOU DIDN'T THINK THAT I WOULD HEAR IT]]', and various other [[emo|shitty]] songs everyone hates.

==[[DEATH]]==
WHEN I WAS died, along with Gerard Way, on November 27th, 2007.
[[Image:Dying.JPG|center]]
[[Image:Dying2.JPG|center]]

